BIDMC PPG and Respiration Dataset — local cache
================================================

This directory contains a small subset of the BIDMC PPG and Respiration Dataset
(records bidmc01, bidmc02, bidmc03), cached locally for CI and offline reproduction.

Citation (required)
-------------------
Pimentel, M. A. F., Johnson, A. E. W., Charlton, P. H., Birrenkott, D., Watkinson,
P. J., Tarassenko, L., & Clifton, D. A. (2017). Toward a robust estimation of
respiratory rate from pulse oximeters. IEEE Transactions on Biomedical Engineering,
64(8), 1914–1923. https://doi.org/10.1109/TBME.2016.2613124

Goldberger, A. L., Amaral, L. A. N., Glass, L., Hausdorff, J. M., Ivanov, P. Ch.,
Mark, R. G., Mietus, J. E., Moody, G. B., Peng, C.-K., & Stanley, H. E. (2000).
PhysioBank, PhysioToolkit, and PhysioNet: Components of a new research resource
for complex physiologic signals. Circulation, 101(23), e215–e220.

