What's included
---------------
bidmc{01,02,03}.dat       — waveform binary (PLETH, RESP, ECG channels, 125 Hz)
bidmc{01,02,03}.hea       — WFDB header
bidmc_csv/bidmc_{01,02,03}_Numerics.csv — 1 Hz HR/RR/SpO2 reference values

What's not included
-------------------
The remaining 50 BIDMC records, the .breath annotation files, and bidmcNNn.* (numerics
in WFDB binary). Fetch the full dataset locally via:
  uv run python -c "import wfdb; wfdb.dl_database('bidmc', 'data/bidmc_cache')"
